items.description:
Color Splash is an application for editing a photo and giving it a certain charm. If you want, you can leave the accented object in color, thus you will make the audience pay attention to it. 
Features:
An intuitive and simple interface;
One-touch control on the screen;
Presence of gestures and scaling;
Built-in video instructions for using the program;
Ability to share edited photos with friends on social networks or Sending by e-mail
Saving an unfinished session and then continuing it
Adjusting the size of the movie and customize the toolbar.
